description:
Designed for long rides and multi-day adventures in all conditions. The Redwood is the ultimate enduro jersey because it’s not always sunny when you want to ride.
Redwood uses Mons Royale's Merino Air-Con 140. Nature's climate control - It keeps you cool when you're hot, warm when its not.
name: Mons Royale Redwood Enduro VLS - AOP - Mens
